<p class="eyebrow"><a href="/integrators/">For integrators</a> / Numbers</p>
<h1>Bring the numbers. Keep the customers.</h1>
<p class="lede">VoiceTel supports local DIDs, toll-free and mobile numbers where available, porting, CNAM and caller-ID services, e911, and numbering APIs. Numbers can be attached to VoiceML, SIP trunks, Hosted PBX, messaging, and lookup workflows.</p>
<p>VoiceTel's <a href="/numbers/">numbers and porting process</a> is built around eligibility checks, LOA preparation, losing-carrier coordination, test windows, rollback planning, and e911 record preparation before the port completes.</p>
<p>For resellers, that matters. Number migration is often where customer trust is won or lost.</p>
<p class="hero-actions">
	<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact/">Become a partner</a>
	<a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/numbers/">Numbers overview</a>
</p>

